entry.title: My Life
entry.summary: Birds is Just Not Fly, They Falled and Try Again
entry.content:
I meshed up tonight, I know I have failed. Some times I felt that I might be better to surrender, take off all the heavy problems have been hanging on my shoulder. But I know I have to get up, start again from the beginning until reach the end.

Keep doing same mistakes again and again
